/target
Cargo.lock.bak
**/*.rs.bk
*.swp
.DS_Store

# Agent harness output (generated, not committed)
.agent/
.archive/

# envctl.lock IS committed — it is the content-hashed manifest-of-record and the
# baseline for `envctl lock --check` (the CI drift gate). Do not ignore it.

# .handoff loop control sentinels — transient, NOT committed. The durable audit trail
# (backlog.md / loop_state.md / HANDOFF.md / cycle/) IS committed so a fresh session resumes cold.
.handoff/loop/DONE
.handoff/loop/NEEDS-HUMAN
.handoff/loop/STOP
# ADR-0004 fail-safe: a per-repo .handoff is git-committed TEXT ONLY — the witnessed ledger lives
# at $META_ROOT/.handoff/ledger.db, never here. Never commit a binary ledger into this repo.
.handoff/**/ledger.db
